0:00:15.26,000 --> 0:00:16,000
We grew up

2
0:00:17.26,000 --> 0:00:19,000
interacting with the physical objects around us.

3
0:00:20.26,000 --> 0:00:23,000
There are an enormous number of them that we use every day.

4
0:00:24.553,000 --> 0:00:26,000
Unlike most of our computing devices,

5
0:00:27.26,000 --> 0:00:29,000
these objects are much more fun to use.

6
0:00:31.18,000 --> 0:00:33,000
When you talk about objects,

7
0:00:33.26,000 --> 0:00:35,000
one other thing automatically comes attached to that thing,

8
0:00:36.26,000 --> 0:00:37,000
and that is gestures:

9
0:00:38.26,000 --> 0:00:39,000
how we manipulate these objects,

10
0:00:40.26,000 --> 0:00:42,000
how we use these objects in everyday life.

11
0:00:43.26,000 --> 0:00:45,000
We use gestures not only to interact with these objects,

12
0:00:46.26,000 --> 0:00:48,000
but we also use them to interact with each other.

13
0:00:48.57,000 --> 0:00:51,000
